'''Jennifer Seiden Sadler''' (born [[August 12]], [[1973]]) worked at [[West End Games]] from [[1996]] to [[1998]]. She was married and legally changed her last name to Schoonover in [[2003]], then divorced and remarried again in 2013. In [[June]] [[2005]], Sadler created the independent publishing company FireWater Productions. She's been a freelancer since 2004 and has works under a myriad of last names.

